html.body: P21CIP module p21CIP1 is regulated in a similar fashion as for p27KIP1, except for its phosphorylation and degradation mediated by CycE1/CDK2. It also binds to CycD1/CDK4,6 and stabilizes the complex whereas it inhibits CycE1/CDK2 and CycA2/CDK2. p21CIP1 seems to inhibit CycB1/CDC2 as well (PMID:16775416).
